column1: The list of all 393 3-round trail cores up to weight 40.
Each 3-line group represents a 3-round trail core.
The first line of each group represents the weight.
The second line represents the position of active bits at a0.
The third line represents the position of active bits at a1.
Each 3-round trail core can easily be generated by knowing the value of a0 and a1.
